title: CAPCOM Monster Hunter Stories - Standard Edition Japanese Ver.(Does not work on USA 3DS/DSI/X)(Japanese Language Only)
description: Platform: Nintendo 3DS Media: Video Game The monster "Otomon" who tied up awakens the hidden ability. Let's make various Otomon companions, and travel together for adventure. In this work there is a character making element of the hero who will be the part of the player. You can customize your sex, appearance, and name to your preference and empathize more. While advancing the story, you can also order an "subquest". Like the conventional Monster Hunter series, there are plenty of elements that can be played.
